0.03    2006-08-09

- This module could overwrite if it was in buffered mode and it sent
  mail as a script exited. Reported by Dean Kopesky.


0.02    2006-07-12

- Make all the tests skip if we don't have Email::Send::Test.

- Add a build_requires prereq on Email::Send::Test.

- Require Email::Send 2.0+ and use its new OO API.

- The mailer_args parameter was being ignored entirely.


0.01    2005-04-11

- First release.
